  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support to the promotion and protection of human rights in Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, OHCHR-Burundi will provide technical assistance and training for local partners, by building their capacity to provide services, in compliance with international human rights standards. These include medical, legal, psychological and socio-economic support to victims and witnesses of human rights violations, including victims of SGBV who require particular attention.OHCHR-Burundi will also build the capacity of CSOs, journalists, and human rights defenders.</narrative>
  </description>
